out_to_x no
background no
cpu_avg_samples 2
net_avg_samples 2
no_buffers yes
out_to_console yes
out_to_stderr no
extra_newline no
update_interval 1.0
uppercase no
use_spacer none

TEXT
^fg(red)BATT:^fg(green)$battery_short $battery_time  ^fg(red)light:^fg(green)$intel_backlight  ^fg(red)RAM:^fg(green)$memperc% \
 ^fg(red)CPU:^fg(green)$cpu%  ^fg(red)Net:^fg(green)${wireless_essid wlp3s0}{$wireless_bitrate wlp3s0}  ^fg(cyan)$distribution \
 ^fg(yellow)${time %a.%d.%m.%Y  %R}  ^fg(magenta)$mpd_status$mpd_smart

